UdsPlusFhirIg

The official URL for this implementation guide is: 

http://fhir.org/guides/hrsa/uds-plus/ImplementationGuide/fhir.hrsa.uds-plus

A brief description of what udsplus is about (probably the same text as in your readme)

name: UdsPlusFhirIg
title: HRSA 2023 Uniform Data System (UDS) Patient Level Submission (PLS) (UDS+) FHIR IG
description: A brief description of what udsplus is about (probably the same text as in your readme)

resource.name: Uds Plus Data Receiver CapabilityStatement

resource.name: UDS Plus Agriculter Worker Status Codes
resource.description: The UDS Plus CodeSystem is a 'starter set' of codes supported for identifying agriculture worker status for UDS+ program.

resource.name: UDS Plus Housing Status Codes
resource.description: The UDS Plus CodeSystem is a 'starter set' of codes supported for identifying Housing status of patients in UDS+ program.

resource.name: UDS Plus Insurance Codes
resource.description: The UDS Plus CodeSystem is a 'starter set' of codes supported for identifying insurance types used by patients in UDS+ program.

resource.name: UDS Plus Housing Service Delivery Codes
resource.description: The UDS Plus CodeSystem is an 'addition set' of one code to the existing Location Service Delivery Codes value set for UDS+ purposes.

resource.name: Generate De-Identified data
resource.description: Generates de-identified  data from identifiable data. The de-identification algorithm to be used is left to the implementers of the operation. Errors during the execution of the operation can be returned as OperationOutcome per the FHIR spec as a return parameter.

resource.name: UDS Plus Import
resource.description: Notification from a Health Center about the availability of the data to HRSA using Bulk Import mechanism.

resource.name: De-Identified UDS Plus AdverseEvent
resource.description: The UDS+ profile is based on the AdverseEvent resource and establishes the core elements, extensions, vocabularies and value sets for representing Allergies and Intolerances for UDS+ program.

resource.name: UDS Plus Age Extension
resource.description: Indicates the age of the patient at a specific time

resource.name: De-Identified UDS Plus AllergyIntolerance
resource.description: The UDS+ profile is based on the AllergyIntolerance resource and establishes the core elements, extensions, vocabularies and value sets for representing Allergies and Intolerances for UDS+ program.

resource.name: UDS Plus Birth Sex Extension
resource.description: Indicates the birth sex of the patient

resource.name: UDS Plus Capitated Member Months Extension
resource.description: Indicates the number of capitated member months of the patient for the reporting year

resource.name: De-Identified UDS Plus Clinical Result Observation
resource.description: The UDS+ profile is based on the Observation resource and establishes the core elements, extensions, vocabularies and value sets for representing clinical result observations for UDS+ program.

resource.name: DeIdentified UDS Plus Coverage
resource.description: The UDS+ profile establishes the core elements, extensions, vocabularies and value sets for representing Coverage for UDS+ program.

resource.name: UDS Plus DeIdentify Data Urls Parameter
resource.description: The UDS+ profile is based on the **Parameters FHIR Resource and establishes the core elements, extensions, vocabularies and value sets for representing the data for sending input and receiving output for the DeIdentify operation of UDS+ .

resource.name: De-Identified UDS Plus Diagnosis
resource.description: The UDS+ profile is based on the Condition resource and establishes the core elements, extensions, vocabularies and value sets for representing Diagnosis for UDS+ program.

resource.name: De-Identified UDS Plus Encounter
resource.description: The UDS+ profile is based on the Encounter resource and establishes the core elements, extensions, vocabularies and value sets for representing encounters,visit information for UDS+ program.

resource.name: UDS Plus Ethnicity Extension
resource.description: Indicates the ethnicity of the patient.

resource.name: UDS Plus FeeForService Member Months Extension
resource.description: Indicates the number of FeeForService member months of the patient for the reporting year

resource.name: UDS Plus Gender Identity Extension
resource.description: Indicates the gender identity of the patient at a specific time

resource.name: UDS Plus Housing Status Extension
resource.description: Indicates the housing status of the patient at a specific time

resource.name: De-Identified UDS Plus Immunization
resource.description: The UDS+ profile is based on the Immunization resource and establishes the core elements, extensions, vocabularies and value sets for representing immunizations for UDS+ program.

resource.name: De-Identified UDS Plus Income
resource.description: The UDS+ profile is based on the Observation resource and establishes the core elements, extensions, vocabularies and value sets for representing Income ranges for UDS+ program.

resource.name: De-Identified UDS Plus Lab Observation
resource.description: The UDS+ profile is based on the Observation resource and establishes the core elements, extensions, vocabularies and value sets for representing lab observations for UDS+ program.

resource.name: UDS Plus Location
resource.description: Indicates the location where the care was provided

resource.name: De-Identified UDS Plus MedicationRequest
resource.description: The UDS+ profile is based on the MedicationRequest resource and establishes the core elements, extensions, vocabularies and value sets for representing MedicationRequest for UDS+ program.

resource.name: De-Identified UDS Plus MedicationStatement
resource.description: The UDS+ profile is based on the MedicationStatement resource and establishes the core elements, extensions, vocabularies and value sets for representing MedicationStatement for UDS+ program.

resource.name: De-Identified UDS Plus Observation
resource.description: The UDS+ profile is based on the Observation resource and establishes the core elements, extensions, vocabularies and value sets for representing assessments, vitals and other social history observations for UDS+ program.

resource.name: UDS Plus Import Manifest
resource.description: The UDS+ profile is based on the **Parameters FHIR Resource and establishes the core elements, extensions, vocabularies and value sets for representing the Manifest for UDS+ import FHIR Operations.

resource.name: UDS Plus Patient Reporting Parameters
resource.description: The UDS+ profile is based on the **Parameters FHIR Resource and establishes the core elements, extensions, vocabularies and value sets for representing the Patients and if they are counted for the various reports.

resource.name: De-Identified UDS Plus Patient
resource.description: This Patient profile represents a Patient availing HRSA services.

resource.name: De-Identified UDS Plus Procedure
resource.description: The UDS+ profile is based on the Procedure resource and establishes the core elements, extensions, vocabularies and value sets for representing procedures for UDS+ program.

resource.name: UDS Plus Race Extension
resource.description: Indicates the race of the patient.

resource.name: UDS Plus RecordedDate Extension
resource.description: Indicates the recorded date of a clinical event

resource.name: De-Identified UDS Plus RelatedPerson
resource.description: This Patient profile represents a RelatedPerson of a Patient availing HRSA services.

resource.name: De-Identified UDS Plus ServiceRequest
resource.description: The UDS+ profile is based on the ServiceRequest resource and establishes the core elements, extensions, vocabularies and value sets for representing ServiceRequest for UDS+ program.

resource.name: De-Identified UDS Plus Sexual Orientation
resource.description: The UDS+ profile is based on the **US Core Sexual Orientation Observation profile and establishes the core elements, extensions, vocabularies and value sets for representing Sexual Orientation for UDS+ program.

resource.name: UDS Plus Veteran Status Extension
resource.description: Indicates the Veteran status of the patient.

resource.name: UDS Plus Agriculture Worker Status Extension
resource.description: Indicates the agriculture worker status of the patient at a specific time

resource.name: Uds Plus Agriculture Worker Status Codes
resource.description: The Uds Plus Agriculture Worker Status Codes is a 'starter set' of codes for specifying agriculture worker status for Patients.

resource.name: Uds Plus Birth Sex Codes
resource.description: The Uds Plus Birth Sex Codes is a set of codes for identifying the birth sex of Patients.

resource.name: Uds Plus Gender Identity Codes
resource.description: The Uds Plus Gender Identity Codes is a 'starter set' of codes for identifying the gender identity of Patients.

resource.name: Uds Plus Housing Status Codes
resource.description: The Uds Plus Housing Status Codes is a 'starter set' of codes for identifying the Patient's housing status.

resource.name: Uds Plus Insurance Codes
resource.description: The Uds Plus Insurance Codes is a 'starter set' of codes for identifying the source of the insurance for Patients.

resource.name: Uds Plus Service Delivery Codes
resource.description: The UDS Plus CodeSystem is an 'addition set' of one code to the existing Location Service Delivery Codes value set for UDS+ purposes.

resource.name: Uds Plus Sexual Orientation Codes
resource.description: The Uds Plus Sexual Orientation Codes is a 'starter set' of codes for identifying the sexual orientation of Patients.
